Package: lignum
Type: Package
Title: Fast Decision Tree Inference Library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kacper", "Piotrowski", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A high-performance inference library for decision-tree based models, 
    specifically optimized for 'LightGBM' and 'XGBoost'. By implementing a native 
    C++ engine, the package bypasses the performance bottlenecks of standard parsers. 
    It features instant file loading via memory mapping ('mmap'), zero-overhead architecture, 
    and efficient row-major multi-threaded computations using OpenMP to ensure maximum CPU 
    cache efficiency during batch predictions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
